<kos/ChangeRequest/cause/SecurityPatch> a skos:Concept ; rdfs:label "Security Patch"@en ; skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/noria/kos/ChangeRequest/cause> .

# ChangeRequest Status
<kos/ChangeRequest/status/Planned> a skos:Concept ; rdfs:label "Planned"@en ; skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/noria/kos/ChangeRequest/status> .
<kos/ChangeRequest/status/Completed> a skos:Concept ; rdfs:label "Completed"@en ; skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/noria/kos/ChangeRequest/status> .

# ChangeRequest Specification
<kos/ChangeRequest/specification/StandardProcedureA> a skos:Concept ; rdfs:label "Standard Procedure A"@en ; skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/noria/kos/ChangeRequest/specification> .

# Resource Type
<kos/Resource/type/Server> a skos:Concept ; rdfs:label "Server"@en ; skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/noria/kos/Resource/type> .
<kos/Resource/type/Router> a skos:Concept ; rdfs:label "Router"@en ; skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/noria/kos/Resource/type> .
<kos/Resource/type/Switch> a skos:Concept ; rdfs:label "Switch"@en ; skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/noria/kos/Resource/type> .
<kos/Resource/type/VirtualMachine> a skos:Concept ; rdfs:label "Virtual Machine"@en ; skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/noria/kos/Resource/type> .
<kos/Resource/type/Database> a skos:Concept ; rdfs:label "Database Server"@en ; skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/noria/kos/Resource/type> .

# Resource Lifecycle State
<kos/Resource/LifecycleState/InProduction> a skos:Concept ; rdfs:label "In Production"@en ; skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/noria/kos/Resource/LifecycleState> .
<kos/Resource/LifecycleState/Staging> a skos:Concept ; rdfs:label "Staging"@en ; skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/noria/kos/Resource/LifecycleState> .

# Resource Operational State
<kos/Resource/OperationalState/Up> a skos:Concept ; rdfs:label "Up"@en ; skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/noria/kos/Resource/OperationalState> .
<kos/Resource/OperationalState/Down> a skos:Concept ; rdfs:label "Down"@en ; skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/noria/kos/Resource/OperationalState> .
<kos/Resource/OperationalState/Degraded> a skos:Concept ; rdfs:label "Degraded"@en ; skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/noria/kos/Resource/OperationalState> .

# Resource Administrative State
<kos/Resource/AdministrativeState/Enabled> a skos:Concept ; rdfs:label "Enabled"@en ; skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/noria/kos/Resource/AdministrativeState> .
<kos/Resource/AdministrativeState/Disabled> a skos:Concept ; rdfs:label "Disabled"@en ; skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/noria/kos/Resource/AdministrativeState> .

# Notification Event Type
<kos/Notification/EventType/StateChange> a skos:Concept ; rdfs:label "State Change Event"@en ; skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/noria/kos/Notification/EventType> .
