# Example of a network interface being a property
:NetworkInterface_DNS_Eth0 a noria:Property . # This is incorrect, NetworkInterface is a StructuralElement, not a Property.
# Correcting: NetworkInterface is a StructuralElement, not a Property.
# Properties are things like noria:networkInterfaceAdministrativeStatus, noria:networkInterfaceOperationalStatus, etc.
# These are properties of the NetworkInterface, not the NetworkInterface itself.

# Example of element property
:Resource_DNS_Server_01 noria:elementProperty :NetworkInterface_DNS_Eth0 . # This is also incorrect. noria:elementProperty relates an Element to a Property.
# Correcting: noria:elementProperty relates an Element to a Property.
# For example, :Resource_DNS_Server_01 noria:elementProperty :NetworkInterface_DNS_Eth0_OperationalStatus . (if I had defined a class for operational status)
# Or, more simply, the properties like noria:networkInterfaceOperationalStatus are sub-properties of noria:structuralElementObservable, which is a sub-property of noria:elementProperty.
# So, :NetworkInterface_DNS_Eth0 noria:networkInterfaceOperationalStatus <kos/Resource/OperationalState/Up> implicitly uses noria:elementProperty.

# Example of element distinguished name
:Resource_DNS_Server_01 noria:elementDistinguishedName "dns01.corp.example.com" .

# Example of element managed by
:Resource_DNS_Server_01 noria:elementManagedBy :Agent_IT_Ops_Team .

# Example of structural element observable
:NetworkInterface_DNS_Eth0 noria:structuralElementObservable <kos/Resource/OperationalState/Up> . # This is implicitly done via noria:networkInterfaceOperationalStatus.

# Example of structural observable of
# This is the inverse of structuralElementProperty, which is not directly used.
# noria:structuralObservableOf is inverse of noria:structuralElementProperty.
# noria:structuralElementProperty is not defined as a direct property, but noria:structuralElementObservable is a sub-property of noria:elementProperty.
# Let's assume a direct instance of a StructuralObservable for demonstration.
:OperationalStatus_DNS_Eth0 a noria:StructuralObservable ;
    rdfs:label "Operational Status of DNS Eth0"@en ;
    noria:structuralObservableOf :NetworkInterface_DNS_Eth0 .

